@martinwicke, @ilblackdragon, @caisq - I need help here. There were no errors but only two TIMEOUT errors when i run

tensorflow/tools/ci_build/ci_build.sh CPU bazel test //tensorflow/...

But I am absolutely unable to figure out why sanity checks are failing only for datafeeder.py. The complain seems to be about Bad indentation. But when I compare for instance other file like graph_io.py, indentation looks same to me. Further more, if I run pylint with ci_build/pep8 configuration file, then the same indentation errors appear for pretty much all other files in Tensorflow (which I did not modify).

I really need some input from you.
